Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:44.07,EDRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}soredemo I’m alright koi no yukue nante
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:48.40,EDRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}mada it isn’t the last chance for me
